Dialogue: 1,0:23:05.93,0:23:08.58,ed_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}我就在这里
Dialogue: 1,0:23:08.58,0:23:13.56,ed_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}有谁笑了
Dialogue: 1,0:23:14.00,0:23:16.42,ed_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}所以你划出了
Dialogue: 1,0:23:16.59,0:23:18.91,ed_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}那条境界线
Dialogue: 1,0:23:19.26,0:23:24.10,ed_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}既然这样 就由我来
Dialogue: 1,0:23:24.16,0:23:27.55,ed_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}牵着你的手
Dialogue: 1,0:23:28.59,0:23:33.11,ed_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}带你一起去
Dialogue: 1,0:23:35.58,0:23:39.22,ed_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}如果说不出口
Dialogue: 1,0:23:39.60,0:23:44.42,ed_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}就紧紧地握住我的手
Dialogue: 1,0:23:44.80,0:23:46.38,ed_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}不要放开
